OL,3,CCouncil's credit rating withdrawn amid
OL,4,Cnear #2 billion debts
OL,6,FInfluential ratings agency Moody's has
OL,7,Fpulled its credit rating of
OL,8,FWarrington's heavily indebted council.
OL,10,FWarrington Borough Council told
OL,11,Fbondholders the agency withdrew its
OL,12,Frating due to "the inability of the
OL,13,Fcouncil to procure that its statements
OL,14,Fof accounts are audited by external
OL,15,Fauditors".
OL,17,FThe Labour-led council has a debt of
OL,18,F#1.85 billion and has come under
OL,19,Fscrutiny for a number of investments.
