OL,3,CCouncil's credit rating withdrawn amid
OL,4,Cnear #2 billion debts
OL,6,FIn May, the Financial Times reported
OL,7,Fthe local authority in Cheshire had
OL,8,Frefused to hand key information to its
OL,9,Fauditor, Grant Thornton, restricting
OL,10,Fits ability to review its books.
OL,12,FThe Government appointed an inspector
OL,13,Fin May to investigate whether the
OL,14,Fcouncil is complying with legal
OL,15,Frequirements after a review last year
OL,16,Fcriticised its "very large and
OL,17,Funiquely complex" set of debt-fuelled
OL,18,Finvestments.
