OL,3,CCouncil's credit rating withdrawn amid
OL,4,Cnear #2 billion debts
OL,6,FAuditors have only recently finished
OL,7,Freviewing Warrington's accounts for
OL,8,Fthe year ending March 31 2019, meaning
OL,9,Fit is reporting years behind legal
OL,10,Frequirements.
OL,12,FThe council said it has been unable to
OL,13,Fcomplete recent audits "due to
OL,14,Fchallenges which apply across the
OL,15,Flocal government sector as a whole in
OL,16,Fsecuring auditors of sufficient
OL,17,Fcapacity and capability".
OL,19,FIt added that it is seeking to secure
OL,20,Fan alternative rating from another EU-
OL,21,Frecognised ratings agency.
