OL,3,CCouncil's credit rating withdrawn amid
OL,4,Cnear #2 billion debts
OL,6,FWarrington Borough Council has built
OL,7,Fup its debts amid a raft of
OL,8,Finvestments in a roughly #1.5 billion
OL,9,Fportfolio, which included now-
OL,10,Fcollapsed energy firm Together Energy.
OL,12,FIt has also reportedly provided loans
OL,13,Fto ecommerce entrepreneur Matthew
OL,14,FMoulding to fund a property deal for
OL,15,Fhis THG business.
OL,17,FIts investments also include a number
OL,18,Fof supermarkets in Greater Manchester
OL,19,Fand solar farms in York and East
OL,20,FYorkshire.
