OL,6,FA Warrington Borough Council
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "Warrington is one
OL,8,Fof only a small number of councils
OL,9,Fwith a credit rating.
OL,11,F"Like other councils across the
OL,12,Fcountry, we have been impacted by the
OL,13,Fnational issue of delays in the
OL,14,Fsigning off of council accounts.
