OL,6,F"Moody's themselves have been clear
OL,7,Fthat the limited prospects towards a
OL,8,Ftimely resolution of the audit backlog
OL,9,Facross the entire local authority
OL,10,Fsector means that, in our case, they
OL,11,Fhave insufficient information to
OL,12,Fmaintain the ratings. They have
OL,13,Ftherefore made the decision to
OL,14,Fwithdraw our credit rating."
